  "text": "To obtain a calibration curve for formaldehyde vapour, standard gaseous formaldehyde was generated according to the reaction described given by Dong and Dasgupta at 20C [CITATION_1] , where aqueous formaldehyde is used to generate equilibrium concentrations of gaseous formaldehyde Eqn 1.",
